{"000-section": {"000-title": "CM\u2019s Business Interest Relief Scheme Launched in Jammu & Kashmir Budget 2018-19"}, "001-section": {"000-title": "CM\u2019s Business Interest Relief Scheme \u2013 Details", "001-normal": "The important features and highlights of this scheme are as follows:-", "002-listElement": "- Under this scheme, the state govt. will pay one third while borrowers have to pay two-third of the monthly installment.", "003-listElement": "- J&K govt. will provide this amount from CM\u2019s Relief Fund and PM Interest Subvention Scheme.", "004-listElement": "- This scheme is applicable for 2 calendar years i.e from Jan 2018 to Jan 2020.", "005-listElement": "- Accordingly, this scheme will benefit several industries, trade bodies and business fraternity and will also give them fiscal space.", "006-listElement": "- Moreover, various banks will also get benefited from this scheme as this scheme will help banks in their Non Performing Assets (NPA) build up.", "007-listElement": "- Banks can avail these benefits only after a percentage point reduction in the average interest rate on the restructured folder."}}